  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you awake, or still dreaming?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You’re on a bus, trying to reach your next stop. But every time you close your eyes, reality shifts.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can you tell what’s real and what’s a nightmare?</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Look for clues</strong> to figure out if you're still dreaming.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Make the right choices</strong> to escape—or stay trapped.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Face unpredictable nightmares</strong> where nothing is as it seems.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297730/extras/a19b87cf1e1878c2708c08342377d648.avif?t=1759167270\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297730/extras_big/a19b87cf1e1878c2708c08342377d648.avif?t=1759167270 width=800 height=450 /></span></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Playtime<strong>:</strong> </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >30-60 minutes</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297730/extras/94608cbca768dd248d12219bcaaa92d2.avif?t=1759167270\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297730/extras_big/94608cbca768dd248d12219bcaaa92d2.avif?t=1759167270 width=800 height=450 /></span></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Difficulty Levels:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Easy:</strong> 1 minute before each blink. Sitting in a chair gives you more time.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Normal:</strong> 1 minute before each blink. Escaping a nightmare might lead to another one.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Insanity:</strong> Every failed escape throws you into a new nightmare. Escaping one brings you back to the last—stay focused.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297730/extras/c925df6ad57c389bd4620091a114754b.avif?t=1759167270\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297730/extras_big/c925df6ad57c389bd4620091a114754b.avif?t=1759167270 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul>",
